></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">{#3}Буйруқ рақами</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-4\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">{#4}Буйруқ қабул қилинган жой</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\"> </span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">Товар моддий қимматликларни хатловдан ўтказиш тўғрисида</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">Бюджет ташкилотларида Бухгалтерия ҳисоби тўғрисидаги йўриқномани тасдиқлаш ҳақидаги Ўзбекистон Республикаси Молия вазирининг 2010 йил </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">17 декабрдаги 105-сон буйруғи, Ўзбекистон Республикаси Адлия вазирлиги томонидан 2010 йил 22 декабрдаги 2169-сон билан рўйхатдан ўтказилган йўриқноманинг 9-бандига мувофиқ, </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">БУЮРАМАН</span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\"> </span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\"> </span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 37.733333333333px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">.</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">{#6}Товар моддий бойликлар хатловдан ўтказилиши белгиланган ташкилот</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">да сақланаётган товар моддий бойликлар хатловдан ўтказилсин.</span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 37.733333333333px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> </span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 37.733333333333px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">.</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\"> Товар моддий бойликларни хатловдан ўтказиш бўйича комиссия таркиби </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">иловага</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\"> мувофиқ тасдиқлансин.</span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 37.733333333333px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> </span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 37.733333333333px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">3. Хатловдан ўтказиш тадбирлари </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">{#7}Товар моддий бойликлар хатловдан ўтказиладиган кунлар давомийлиги</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\"> кунлари амалга оширилсин ва хатлов маълумотлари ташкилотнинг бош ҳисобчисига топширилсин.</span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 37.733333333333px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> </span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 37.733333333333px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">Асос:</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> Бюджет ташкилотларида Бухгалтерия ҳисоби тўғрисидаги йўриқномани тасдиқлаш ҳақидаги Ўзбекистон Республикаси Молия вазирининг 2010 йил 17 декабрдаги 105-сон буйруғи, Ўзбекистон Республикаси Адлия вазирлиги томонидан 2010 йил 22 декабрдаги 2169-сон билан рўйхатдан ўтказилган йўриқноманинг 9-банди, бош ҳисобчи билдиришномаси.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<table style=\"border: 0px solid; border-spacing: 0; \">\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">{#8}Буйруқ чиқарган шахснинг лавозими</span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">_______________</span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">{#9}Буйруқ чиқарган шахснинг Ф.И.О.си</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>(имзо)</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">ИЛОВА</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Товар моддий бойликларни хатловдан ўтказиш бўйича комиссия таркиби</span></p>\n<table style=\"border: 0px solid; border-spacing: 0; \">\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 310.60387811634px;\">\n<p><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#10}Ходимнинг Ф.И.О си</span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 310.6703601108px;\">\n<p><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#11}Ходимнинг лавозими</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n</div></div>",
